main_body:
Article 3 of Regulation (EC) No 596/2004 is hereby amended as follows:
1. Paragraph 4 is replaced by the following:
(a) set a single acceptance percentage for the quantities applied for;
(b) reject applications for which licences have not yet been granted;
(c) suspend the lodging of licence applications for a maximum period of five working days, extendable by the procedure specified in Article 17 of Regulation (EEC) No 2771/75.
2. The following paragraph 4a is inserted:
